          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "ChatGPT can write blog posts, but it has no SEO capabilities — no keyword research, no SERP analysis, no content scoring, no competitive data. Every SEO element must be added manually. For consistent SEO content production, dedicated tools like Surfer SEO, Frase, or theStacc save significantly more time." }
